articles.title: Photo calorie app Cal AI, downloaded over a million times, was built by two teenagers - TechCrunch
articles.description: Cal AI has generated over 5 million downloads in 8 months, it says. Founders Zach Yadegari and Henry Langmack are just 18.
articles.content:
In a world filled with vibe coding, Zach Yadegari, teen founder of Cal AI, stands in ironic, old-fashioned contrast. 
Ironic because Yadegari and his co-founder, Henry Langmack, are both just 18 yea… [+3790 chars]
